caption.text:
This is why your posts aren’t going viral📲

This is essential, so make sure you save this post for later…

You’re not telling a story.📚

People genuinely won’t care about you, your content or your brand if you don’t master STORYTELLING…

There are 7 elements to a good story✅

You need: 

- A hero (the customer)
- A problem for the hero
- A mentor (you) to guide the hero
- A plan
- A call to action that creates urgency
- Stakes (what happens if they fail)
- Payoff (what happens if they succeed)

Unless you have all of these elements in your content, there’s not really a reason for your viewer to care…

I learned this is the book: Building a Story Brand📕

I’m going to create a full breakdown of it in my next video so stick around for it🔎
